	<HediffDef>
		<defName>APM_DuelDraw</defName>
		<label>duel draw</label>
		<hediffClass>HediffWithComps</hediffClass>
		<description>The duel ended without a victor. Both combatants stood when the arena fell — a dishonor neither can easily shake. Movement is sluggish as though the shame of an unresolved contest weighs heavily on the body. The debuff will lift in time but the stigma of a draw is not quickly forgotten.</description>
		<isBad>true</isBad>
		<stages>
			<li>
				<capMods>
					<li>
						<capacity>Moving</capacity>
						<offset>-0.15</offset>
					</li>
					<li>
						<capacity>Manipulation</capacity>
						<offset>-0.10</offset>
					</li>
					<li>
						<capacity>Consciousness</capacity>
						<offset>-0.10</offset>
					</li>
				</capMods>
			</li>
		</stages>
		<comps>
			<li Class="HediffCompProperties_Disappears">
				<disappearsAfterTicks>60000~120000</disappearsAfterTicks>
				<showRemainingTime>True</showRemainingTime>
			</li>
			<li Class="HediffCompProperties_DisappearsOnDeath" />
		</comps>
	</HediffDef>
</Defs>